"USCIS created the Fraud Detection and National Security (FDNS) Directorate to strengthen the integrity of the nation’s immigration system and to ensure that immigration benefits are not granted to individuals that may pose a threat to national security and/or public safety. In the future, there are plans to integrate AI/ML into the predictive modeling for future system enhancements, working side-by-side with the business stakeholders to develop best practices.
